      "lineNumber": 7,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "The Stage 2 marquee row at the goal surface. 3_000_000_000 \u002B 2_000_000_000\noverflows uint(uint.MaxValue ~ 4.29e9). Under Way 3 the addition promotes\nto BigInteger, computes 5_000_000_000, and narrows the result to long \u2014\nno silent uint wrap. The goal test pins the sum\u0027s value; the kind-on-the-\nresult test (\u0060%sum.Type.Kind%\u0060 == \u0022long\u0022) sits in C# NumberArithmeticTests.",
